Title: The Halo Mass Function of Late-Type Galaxies from HI Kinematics
Authors: P. Li, F. Lelli, S.S. McGaugh, M.S. Pawlowski, M. Zwaan, J.M. Schombert
================================================================================
Byte-by-byte Description of file: HMF_NFW.mrt
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
   Bytes Format Units         Label     Explanations
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
   1-  7 F7.3   solMass       log(M200) Log of the dark-matter halo mass (1)
   8- 13 F5.2   Mpc^-3        log(Phi)  Number of halos per unit volume
  14- 18 F4.2   Mpc^-3    eup_log(Phi)  Upper error on log(Phi)
  19- 23 F4.2   Mpc^-3    elo_log(Phi)  Lower error on log(Phi) 
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
(1) This is the central value of the mass bin
